  "description": "<i>Witches' Brew Adventure</i> is the eleventh in a series of monthly text adventures for multiple systems.<br><br>You have just arrived in an enchanted forest, and your goal is to rescue the princess.  The player must explore a witches' cottage, which contains numerous magical items and secrets, as well as the surrounding forest and mountains.  The goal is to gather the necessary ingredients to create three magical potions, the brews of invisibility, shrinking, and growth.  Using the player's wits and these magical ingredients, they player must plant a beanstalk to allow them access to the giant's castle high in the sky.  There, they must outsmart the giant and rescue to princess imprisoned within the castle.  Dangers include the witch of the cottage, her cat, a malevolent axeman, wild animals, and the giant who live up in the sky.  <br><br>All commands are via 2-word VERB NOUN entries, and game play contains several object puzzles. There is a save and restore feature.",
